strings: <voice_0x01000FF8><se_def>Dalmatian: Alright! This bastard is following me!
<voice_0x01000FF9><se_def>Dalmatian: If I remember correctly, you were the walking scarecrow I met in Muncharoga Mare.
<voice_0x01000FFA><se_def>Dalmatian: Is this true! Do you think you can defeat me and break the curse of God?
<voice_0x01000FFB><se_def>Dalmatian: Meaning<:> Ha, ha, ha! Please do your best. Sorry. Currently not accepting visitors.
<voice_0x01000FFC><se_def>Dalmatian: I'm getting better, but my body can't stand it. This is because magic is very powerful. This is its strength.
<voice_0x01000FFD><se_def>Dalmatian: It's a small price to pay for such incredible power.
<voice_0x01000FFE><se_def>Dalmatian: At least you won't stay long, okay?
<voice_0x01001000><se_def>Dalmatian: I cannot fulfill my Lord's wishes.
<voice_0x01001001><se_def>Dalmatian: But at least you will reach your destiny. die in my hands
<voice_0x01001002><se_def>Dalmatian: Have you learned Will I be back?
<voice_0x01001003><se_def>Dalmatian: In order to bring the master back to normal, Ina-san is trying to get revenge on her brother... but everyone seems to be mourning.
<voice_0x01001004><se_def>Dalmatian: But the worst! No matter how hard I try, I just can't resist!
<voice_0x01001005><se_def>Dalmatian: Do you think you can really fight someone as strong as me? What a stupid loophole!
